**Scenario 2: Remote Image (external URL)**

```tsx
// 1. Configure domains in next.config.js
module.exports = {
  images: {
    remotePatterns: [
      {
        protocol: 'https',
        hostname: 'images.unsplash.com',
      },
    ],
  },
};

// 2. Use in component
import Image from 'next/image';

export default function Gallery() {
  return (
    <Image
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-123"
      alt="Photo"
      width={800}     // Must specify for remote images
      height={600}
      loading="lazy"  // Default (lazy load)
    />
  );
}
```

